 Product Description 
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  For more than 90 years Hallmark has designed greeting cards for life's special moments. Hallmark Card Studio 2009 Deluxe extends this tradition, making it easy to create one-of-a-kind Hallmark cards as unique as the people you care for. In three simple steps you can add personal photos, sentiments and clip art images of your choosing.

Select from thousands of cards, invitations, stickers and more. Click to enlarge.

Commemorate events with custom calendars and more. Click to enlarge.

Easily add your own photos to cards and enhance them using Card Studio's digital photo editor. Click to enlarge.
The #1 Greeting Card Software

Our new Deluxe 2009 version includes:

    * 9,000+ Hallmark Cards and Projects: Design cards for all occasions--birthdays, holidays, weddings and more.

    * 1,200+ New Designs

    * 16,000+ Clip Art Images: Complement your cards with sensational artwork.

    * Brand New Animated User Interface

    * 3D Cards and Projects

    * New--Photo Calendars and Photo Cards

    * Exclusive Hallmark Fonts and Sentiments

    * Event Planner: Stay organized with address books, mailing lists and date notification.

    * Enhanced Digital Photography Features: Easily add your own photos to cards and enhance them using Card Studio's digital photo editor.

    * Hallmark E-Cards: Send your personalized cards and projects via e-mail with just one click

    But cards are just the beginning. Commemorate events and bridge the miles between family and friends with custom calendars, photo frames, stationery, invitations, scrapbooks, certificates and more! It's amazing what you and Hallmark can do together!
Creating Your Own Cards Is Faster, Easier and More Fun than Ever

Create personalized cards in 3 easy steps:

   1. Select from thousands of cards, invitations, stickers and more
   2. Add your own unique message or personal photos. Then change fonts, colors or graphics.
   3. Print, email or create a PDF of your one-of-a-kind creation. 

Personalize cards and projects with your digital photos.

    * Correct any photo, remove red eye and apply special effects with a host of easy-to-use tools in our Digital Photo Editor.
    * Use photos for photo cubes, photo cards, photo calendars, photo frames, and more
